ESMValTool v2.0. VE coordinated the ESMValTool v2.0 release. All other
authors contributed to individual diagnostics for this release. All authors
contributed to the text.</p></div><span class="section6-mobile-bottom-border mobile-bottom-border hide-on-desktop hide-on-tablet"></span></div>
