Soc., 95, 1329–1334, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1175/Bams-D-12-00204.1">https://doi.org/10.1175/Bams-D-12-00204.1</a>, 2014. </span></p><p class="ref" id="bib1.bib64"><span class="mixed-citation">Terzago, S., Palazzi, E., and von Hardenberg, J.: Stochastic downscaling of precipitation in complex orography: a simple method to reproduce a realistic fine-scale climatology, Nat. Hazards Earth Syst. Sci., 18, 2825–2840, <a href="https://doi.org/10.5194/nhess-18-2825-2018">https://doi.org/10.5194/nhess-18-2825-2018</a>, 2018. </span></p><p class="ref" id="bib1.bib65"><span class="mixed-citation">Thornthwaite, C. W.: An Approach toward a Rational Classification of
